abstract: Arab League condemns what they call abduction of at least 26 Qatari hunters in southern Iraq; whereabouts of hunting party, which includes members of senior Qatari royalty, is unknown; situation strains relations between Qatar and Iraq.
lead_paragraph: At least 26 hunters, including senior members of Qatar’s royalty, were taken captive last week in southern Iraq, near the Saudi Arabian border.

headline.main: Arab League Condemns Abduction of Qataris by Armed Group in Iraq
headline.print_headline: Middle East; Arab League Condemns Abduction of Qataris by Armed Group in Iraq
